products.name: Apple Watch Series 6
products.Description: Made from high-quality denim fabric, this midi skirt offers durability and comfort for all-day wear. The mid-length design strikes the perfect balance between casual and chic, making it suitable for various occasions, from casual outings to semi-formal events.               One of the standout features of this skirt is its functional pockets. With two spacious pockets at the front, you can conveniently carry your essentials such as keys, phone, or wallet without the need for a bulky bag. The pockets also add a touch of utility and flair to the overall look.

products.name: DJI Air 2s
products.Description: Intelligent Flight Function. Intelligent Follow 4.0, Points of Interest Surround 3.0, etc., enable the craft to actively follow or fly around the target, and detect and bypass obstacles during flight. Assisted Shooting. Powerful auxiliary shooting functions, such as Master Lens, Time-lapse, and One-Touch Movie, help you make a big movie easily. Gimbal Camera Performance. The 3-axis gimbal camera can stabilize 5.4K 30fps/4K 60fps/1080p120fps Ultra HD video, and shoot up to 20 megapixel photos. It supports shooting 10 bit D-Log M video, which is convenient for color grading later. Graphic Transfer Performance. DJlAir 2S uses 03(0cusync 3.0) mapping technology with built-in 4 antennas.
